.react-fluid-table .cell, .react-fluid-table .header-cell { box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; padding: 8px; }.react-fluid-table-container { will-change: height; }.sticky-header { position: sticky; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; z-index: 1; }.row-wrapper { display: inline-block; }.react-fluid-table-header { display: flex; }.header-cell { -webkit-box-align: baseline; align-items: baseline; }.header-cell-text { font-weight: bold; color: rgb(125, 125, 125); overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }.header-cell-arrow { width: 0px; height: 0px; margin-left: 4px; border-left: 5px solid transparent; border-right: 5px solid transparent; }.header-cell-arrow.asc { border-bottom: 10px solid rgb(125, 125, 125); }.header-cell-arrow.desc { border-top: 10px solid rgb(125, 125, 125); }.react-fluid-table-row { border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236); }.react-fluid-table-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }.react-fluid-table-footer { width: 100%; border-top: 1px solid rgb(236, 236, 236); }.react-fluid-table-footer.sticky { position: sticky; bottom: 0px; left: 0px; z-index: 1; overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; }.react-fluid-table-footer.sticky::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }.row-container { display: flex; }.cell { -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }.expander { cursor: pointer; height: 1em; width: 1em; }.hidden { display: none; }
